**Clairvoyant Fox** | Werewolf Investigative
__Basics__
Each day, the Clairvoyant Fox may ??. Once per game, the Clairvoyant Fox may alternatively join the wolfpack as a regular wolf.
__Details__
Each day, the Clairvoyant Fox may either ?? or choose to join the wolfpack.
The Hosts announce to the wolfpack at the start of each night what ??.
The Clairvoyant Fox and wolfpack do not know each other's identities, as the Clairvoyant Fox is not a lycan, nor a member of the wolfpack. 
If the Clairvoyant Fox chooses to join the wolfpack, they may not ?? that day, and will lose their power as they will become a regular wolf. 
Joining the wolfpack is an immediate ability.
